
zenmon
  rename
=====================

client 
  * use local database
      * --use-local-db switch
      * check for database. Init if not found
  * option to send all/past data
  * --test-server option (data is not added to the database on server)
  * --test option (output json data to stdout and don't send)

db
  * get uuid for node (or create new)
  * insert data (temp_struct)
  * get_data(timeframe)
      * convenience functions
          * 24h
	  * 1 week
	  * 1 month
	  * all

json
  * temp_struct to json
  * temp_struct from json

general
  * give type of sensor information to allow for other sensors

sensor struct base class
  * to_json
  * from_json

temp_struct {
    token
    type
    time
    test bool
    data {
      temperature
    }
}

return_struct {
  success bool
  error string
}

